---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Quantum Technology Applications"
  description="Advanced quantum computing applications for real-world challenges"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Quantum Applications Portfolio</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Quantum Sensing</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• High-precision measurements</li>
          <li>• Quantum radar systems</li>
          <li>• Gravitational sensing</li>
          <li>• Magnetic field detection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Quantum Imaging</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Ghost imaging</li>
          <li>• Quantum microscopy</li>
          <li>• Entangled photon imaging</li>
          <li>• Sub-wavelength resolution</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Quantum Security</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Quantum key distribution</li>
          <li>• Post-quantum cryptography</li>
          <li>• Quantum random numbers</li>
          <li>• Secure communications</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Application Development Process</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Research & Design</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Requirements Analysis</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Detailed assessment of application needs</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Quantum Circuit Design</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Optimized quantum algorithm development</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Implementation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Prototype Development</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Rapid iteration and testing</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">System Integration</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Seamless deployment and optimization</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Success Stories</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Financial Risk Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Implemented quantum algorithms for real-time risk assessment, achieving 100x faster processing compared to classical methods.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-purple-600">Results: 99.9% accuracy • 60% cost reduction</div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Drug Discovery</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Accelerated molecular simulation for drug discovery, reducing research time from years to months.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-purple-600">Results: 80% time savings • 3 promising compounds identified</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Transform Your Applications?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Discover how our quantum technology applications can revolutionize your business processes and unlock new possibilities.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
        Schedule a Demo
      </a>
      <a href="/services/quantum/platforms" class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
        Explore Platforms
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>